metadata.name: Panels 1 | The Ethernals | Comic Gods
metadata.description:
The adventure begins with the Ethernals. Ethernals are mysterious god-like beings that are blamed for ripping a hole in the Multiverse while on a quest for truth and balance. The Multiverse will never be the same! Who are these Ethernals? Are they a threat? Are they a scam?

Panels are animated comic book stories rescued from the Multiverse ether. Researchers are not sure if these digital artifacts are from the past, future, or another reality? These future hieroglyphs Are revealing the weirdest superhero adventure ever. Stay tuned as more panels are being digitally excavated and undeciphered!

It is unknown if any of these panels are related? We are unsure of their purpose, or hidden messages? 

This animated artifact has nostalgic similarities to early Marvel comics and the cosmic art of Jack Kirby.

Comic Gods is a multimedia cryptoart adventure. The Comic Gods multiverse will expand over many marketplaces, and include animations, cover art, panel art, phygital sketches, and .....
